These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, march, october
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, amber, red
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
3 different pets are kept: cat, pony, goldfish
House: victorian, futuristic, modern
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, bus, quad-bike
 1. the person driving the trike is the german##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is the owner of the goldfish##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is between the italian and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 4. the futuristic house is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the owner of the pony is the person who likes red##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the colombian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the victorian house##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Birthday      | march    | october   | may           |
| Color          | amber       | red    | apricot         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Pet           | cat | pony   | goldfish      |
| House   | futuristic        | modern    | victorian       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Transport         | trike     | bus | quad-bike |

