.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, camping, woodworking
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard, car
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, baccarat, bongani
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, rose, orchid
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, june
 1. the person who growsorchid is the baccarat-smoker##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 5. the bongani-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Hobby      | writing   | woodworking    | camping         |
| Transport          | snowmobile    | skateboard | car          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Cigar   | bongani      | baccarat   | swisher    |
| Flower           | dahlia        | orchid      | rose         |
| Birthday         | july | december  | june |

