.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, lavender, azure
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, skydiving
House: wooden, modern, palace
City: boston, hannover, colone
3 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, snooker
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, lemonade
 1. the person who likes lavender is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person playing snooker is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the wooden house is the person who likes azure##1
 4. the modern house is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the modern house is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person playing backgammon and the person traveling to colone##2
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
11. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Color          | azure      | lavender      | white      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| House   | wooden | modern    | palace          |
| City   | hannover       | boston      | colone          |
| Game   | backgammon    | billiard  | snooker      |
| Pet           | hamster   | hedgehog  | mouse        |
| Beverage         | cola  | almond-milk   | lemonade     |

