.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, water-polo, surfing
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, whist
There 3 different types of food: plum, peach, lime
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, light-blue, pink
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, jazz, pop
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, august
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 7. the fan of country is the person playing whist##1
 8. the person eating plum is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person eating plum and the person eating lime##2
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Sport      | badminton | water-polo           | surfing      |
| Game         | domino       | whist         | backgammon       |
| Food           | plum    | peach | lime |
| Color   | chestnut       | pink         | light-blue      |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | country        | jazz          |
| Birthday   | august   | december       | april         |
| Pet           | mouse       | ferret         | lizard        |

