House: farmhouse, futuristic, gothic-revival
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, martial-arts, animation
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, taxi
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 3. the person who growstulip is the person watching animation movies##1
 4. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the vegafina-smoker##2
 6. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching western movies and the gothic-revival house##2
 7. the person driving the bike is between the person eating strawberry and the person who growsiris##2
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
