.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, begonia, iris
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, poker
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, jazz, disco
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, red, grey
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, water-polo
House: futuristic, townhouse, tower
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person playing canasta##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 6. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 7. the tower house is between the person who growstulip and the fan of trance##2
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person playing canasta is the futuristic house##1
10. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes red##1
11. the futuristic house is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
